# login using admin/admin

# now add data source and dashboards as per requirement
# add prometheus as data source using http://prometheus:9090
go to configuration -> data sources -> add data source -> select prometheus -> set url to http://prometheus:9090 -> save & test 
# import dashboards from grafana.com
go to + -> import -> enter dashboard id from grafana.com -> load -> select prometheus as data source -> import

# the dashboards id are 1860 (node exporter), 6417 (cAdvisor), 763 (prometheus) etc.
# now you can monitor your containers using grafana dashboards

